<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="20Nov1934"><font color="red">20 November 1934</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Giorgio Joyce): As reports from Kusnacht are favorable we contemplate going back to Paris though I don&apos;t like leaving Lucia for the Xmas &hellip; I hope you have a pleasant Thanksgiving dinner next Thursday, (22 November 1934) is it? We met Huddleston in Geneva </div>
